snippet.title: Titanfall: Expedition Gameplay Trailer
snippet.description:
Get your first look at how Swampland, Runoff, and War Games add even more action and intensity to the Frontier. 

Titanfall: Expedition DLC will be available for the Xbox One and PC on May 15th and for Xbox 360 in June. http://www.titanfall.com/dlc
